text: Anke Schönfelder (born 2 October 1975) is a German gymnast. She competed in six events at the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1975 births Category:Living people Category:German female artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Germany Category:Gymnasts at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Gymnasts from Berlin
